{"tid":1382830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日要有人係巴士/地鐵守護巴士/地鐵大佬![假設]我認為好大機會有藍絲搞佢!","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T17:09:33.000Z","uid":102343,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"46216ba1dcedc6f8de79259ed93c927af4b4954f","tid":1382830,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:31:09.000Z","msg":"平時係巴士地鐵都見唔少巴絲上連登，求下你地一定要守護好巴士大佬，地鐵大佬。 <br />\n<br />\n我相信大部分藍絲都會工照番! 我地就算罷工都要組隊守護佢地，令佢地影響更多人同有民意基礎進行聽日嘅行動。<br />\n<br />\n前車可鑑，有廢老打巴士大佬，有藍絲打車長。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢需要我地幫佢地拍片做證據同支持，請各位上巴士時同巴士司機講<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加油</span></span>，最好坐下層方便保護佢地比哂signal 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係各地鐵站嘅大家最好坐近車長室果卡，見到佢地換車長時講下<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加油</span></span>，比下signal佢地知有人撐佢同保護佢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位運輸業大佬有行動我地更加要有行動支持同保護佢地!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">多謝你地咁多位運輸業大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"0381a7a4580cf92b0d2b9eaa0948d2d2f96f34b8","tid":1382830,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"86628188416109878a9778ca742c0b9580c1c8aa","tid":1382830,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4098aef1c0a0f6f8c16c792d37dded03c79ab4c3","tid":1382830,"uid":284636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:39:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8b3b63cc68d2e90bdb49af4fd9a2dfd7c64d7dc2","tid":1382830,"uid":102343,"like"